high_descs: Turn and walk to the right. Walk forward to the green chair and turn right again to face the chair.
Pick up the remote that is on the left off off the chair.
Make a right and walk over to the couch and make a left to face it.
Put the remote on to the sofa.
Make a left and walk forward and make a left to face the chair.
Pick up the remote off of the chair.
Make a right and walk over to the couch and make a left to face it.
Place the remote on the sofa to the left of the other remote.
anns.task_desc: Move two remotes to the green sofa.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the chair on the right.
Pick up the remote on the left side of the chair.
Take a few steps right to the couch.
Place the remote on the couch to the left of the box.
Take a few steps left.
Pick up the other remote on the chair.
Take a few steps right.
Place the remote on the couch to the left of the first remote.
anns.task_desc: Place two remotes on a couch.

high_descs: Turn right and walk until you're even with the chair that has two remotes on it's cushion then when you are even with it stop and turn right to face it.
Pick up the remote that's on the left.
Turnright and walk to the middle of the couch that's on your left then whe you get to the middle stop and turn left to face it.
Put the remote vertically on the center cushion near it's front edge.
Go back to where you got the first remote.
Pick up the remote that's in front of you.
Go back to where you put the first remote.
Put this remote the same way on the center cushion about four remote widths to the left of the first.
anns.task_desc: Put two remotes on the couch.
